text: Liomesus is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==Species== Species within the genus Liomesus include: * Liomesus ovum (Turton, 1825) * Liomesus stimpsoni Dall, 1889 ==References== ==External links== * Category:Buccinidae
title: Liomesus
